ISLAMABAD, Aug 03 (APP):President Dr Arif Alvi Monday summoned the session of Senate to meet on Wednesday, August 5, at 10.30 a.m. in the Parliament House.
According to the Senate Secretariat notification, he called the session in exercise of the powers conferred by Clause (1) of Article 54 of the Constitution.
